{"tid":1231623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"親中父母:公投啦！公投最公道！","createTime":"2019-06-16T13:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T13:24:04.000Z","uid":76784,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28cd6180e2ec2c93c8d2b2d2ed990962b3bb3b48","tid":1231623,"uid":76784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:16:27.000Z","msg":"今晚同老頭老母食飯，言語間，他們當然是比較親中，我也無意要改變他們。<br />\n<br />\n但突然間，我老豆老母話，公投啦！公投最公道！唔洗上街搞搞震！<br />\n<br />\n😂😂<br />\n<br />\n我忍唔住讚佢地，原來您地咁民主。但你偉大的黨就係唔會俾您咁做。<br />\n<br />\n其實您倆個應該上街。"},{"pid":"5298e1ab52f57e4ea107fef2c88f1e8836c26a4c","tid":1231623,"uid":90301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"顛覆國家政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbe58bdb10c23776c69999fb0b06bad8c27a02d","tid":1231623,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"真係豬嚟，講過呢啲野送中一過就拉佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}